name: Sense-Data
description:
Reach the exit!

Move with WASD, look with mouse.

This game uses audio samples taken from a recording of Bertrand Russell's "The Problems of Philosophy" which is available under public domain: https://librivox.org/the-problems-of-philosophy-by-bertrand-russell-2/

Various textures were taken from Google images.

Made for the January 2019 Philosophy Game Jam.
